data.text:
King Albert II and Queen Paola Attend Wedding of Princess Maria Laura

Albert II, King Emeritus and Queen Paola, Queen Emerita of Belgium attend the wedding of Princess Maria Laura of Belgium and William Isvy at the St Michael and St Gudula Cathedral on 10 September 2022 in Brussels, Belgium.
